US Transportation sells Automated Solutions . U . S . Transportation Systems Inc said on Monday that it sold one of its manufacturing subsidiaries , Automated Solutions Inc , to KAC Inc , a privately held , Phoenix - based company , for $ 6 . 5 million in cash payable over two years . U . S . Transportation said that the sale will be reported as a pre - tax gain of slightly more than $ 1 . 3 million to be recognized in the first quarter ended March 31 , 1997 . ( ( - - New York Newsdesk 212 859 - 1610 ) ) 
